eview-title\">Quick response</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vettestripes/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08bc7c56a6333ec3678fce177e2da819bfe3a017efe6a7ea3951649c08aa1b0c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08bc7c56a6333ec3678fce177e2da819bfe3a017efe6a7ea3951649c08aa1b0c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vettestripes/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vettestripes</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">15 Червня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I posted my issue and within 10 minutes or so, I got an answer to fix my issue!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you so much!!!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Errores con ultima actualización 9.9.3</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/servimatrixproductos/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18322fdc49da6296f07167dac8f3987c084843009b4bcc9911944cf79e2f22c9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18322fdc49da6296f07167dac8f3987c084843009b4bcc9911944cf79e2f22c9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/servimatrixproductos/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">servimatrixproductos</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">15 Червня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Al actualizar plugin 9.9.3 se producen problemas GRAVES. Se ocultan categorías y subcategorías de los productos. Esto provoca un desorden general. Intenté solucionarlo de diferentes maneras pero no lo logré. Mi única solución fue devolver a la versión anterior 9.8.5.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">limited with free features</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rudsonalex/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/faffdf97495ffb60e45595e7c4f06ec959ad43a5afbe6fe9200e51d8c325823b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/faffdf97495ffb60e45595e7c4f06ec959ad43a5afbe6fe9200e51d8c325823b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rudsonalex/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rudsonalex</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">15 Червня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Good, but very limited with free features, especially regarding the members area…</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Well done! (Never forget it&#039;s free)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thomhsb/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9b33cdf25014dcb30148784e10c39221353457dd8503d4e15613eb6226fa7efd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9b33cdf25014dcb30148784e10c39221353457dd8503d4e15613eb6226fa7efd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thomhsb/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Thomas <small>(thomhsb)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">15 Червня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Personally, I think this plugin is excellent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When I sometimes see the very poor ratings, I tell myself that these people have quickly forgotten that this plugin is open source and that they don\'t pay a cent to use it. On the contrary, they\'re making money with it...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So yes, there are occasional bugs, and yes, some updates make the system unstable.<br />And yes, that\'s annoying! But rather than giving the plugin a one-star rating at this point - when they hadn\'t bothered to rate it when everything was going well - just go back to the previous version, nothing so catastrophic.<br />Then alert the technical team, who are doing their best in view of the many differences between installations and other plugins. All that\'s left to do is wait, and hope, as I did, that the next update will have corrected the previous problems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Of course, I\'m also annoyed to see all the work done upstream broken after a simple update! Of course, sometimes the answers aren\'t the right ones. But they answer, and try to understand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As an amateur developer, I never forget just how titanic the work is, and that my overall configuration isn\'t necessarily the best either. We use hooks, modify certain zones to customize the layout, and so on.<br /><br />In conclusion, I\'m not lecturing anyone, I\'m just trying to remind people that the product they sometimes complain about is free and that technical support has no obligation after all... So, I just like the idea of encouraging them rather than denigrating them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Quick and good answers.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trevellfr/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cf2c3ea875b9eebe392c8ccf3ef2144fac1023f409708fdf6bb3a9c914a3c23a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cf2c3ea875b9eebe392c8ccf3ef2144fac1023f409708fdf6bb3a9c914a3c23a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trevellfr/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">trevellfr</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">13 Червня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I contact the support for an issue about critical error and in a few days a solution was found !</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:296:\"Все, що вам потрібно, щоб відкрити інтернет-магазин за кілька днів і підтримувати його розвиток роками. Від вашого першого продажу до мільйонного доходу Woo з вами.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.9.9.4.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}